  "rawText": "=== 第1页 ===\nU1 基础知识——重点短语\ntake care of\ncome from be from be from be from\nkeep warm\nbe good for be good for be good for\nlook like\nin the sea\nblack and white\npick up\neach other\nlook after\nin danger\ncut down\ntoo much\nbe made of\nquite a\nnot at all\n1. 照顾；处理\n2. 来自\n3. 保持温暖\n4. 对......有好处\n5. 看起来像\n6. 在海里\n7. 黑白相间的\n8. 拿起\n9. 互相\n10. 照顾\n11. 处于危险之中\n12. 砍伐，减少\n13. 太多\n14. 由... ... 制成的\n15. 相当；非常\n16. 一点也不；完全不\n\n=== 第2页 ===\n北大附中25级初一（下）英语早读听力练习2\n班级 t(6) 姓名 王浩然\n一、听后选择。\n请听一段对话，完成第1至第2小题。\n(B) 1. Where does the girl think Hammy might be?\nA. In his cage.\nB. In the living room.\nC. In the bathroom.\n(A) 2. What is the girl worried about?\nA. Hammy is lost.\nB. Hammy likes to break toys.\nC. Hammy can't go far.\n请听一段对话，完成第3至第4小题。\n(B) 3. Why does Peter like monkeys?\nA. Because they're very smart.\nB. Because they're very cute.\nC. Because they're very interesting.\n(A) 4. What time do they plan to meet?\nA. At 3:00 p.m.\nB. At 3:30 p.m.\nC. At 4:30 p.m.\n请听一段独白，完成第5至第6小题。\n(B) 5. What can we learn from the talk?\nA. Tom lives in a restaurant with his family.\nB. Jerry goes to get food in the evening.\nC. Jerry usually gets up at six in the morning.\n(A) 6. Why does Jerry give the talk?\nA. To talk about his daily life.\nB. To share his eating habits.\nC. To show his family members.\n二、听后回答。\n请听一段对话，回答第7小题。\n7. Where does Coco often sleep?\nOn the sofa.\n请听一段对话，回答第8小题。\n8. Why does the girl like giraffes?\nBecause there are interesting.\n请听一段对话，回答第9小题。\n9. What does Sarah's cat love to do?\nShe loves to sleep and play with the balls.\n请听一段对话，回答第10小题。\n10. What does the man think of elephants?\nThey are smart.\n请听一段对话，回答第11至第12小题。\n11. What is Lily's favourite animal?\nDolphins.\n12. What can dolphins do according to Lily?\nThey are smart and friendly.\nDolphins can jump really high out of the water.",
